```python
import pandas as pd

df = pd.DataFrame({
    "feature": ["F1","F2","F3","F4","F5","F6"],
    "impact":  [120, 80, 60, 40, 30, 20]
})
display(df)
```

# ÌíÄÏù¥

```python
df_ranked = df.sort_values(by='impact', ascending=False)
df_ranked['impact_ratio'] = df_ranked['impact']/sum(df_ranked['impact'])
df_ranked['cum_ratio'] = df_ranked['impact_ratio'].expanding().sum()
key_features = df_ranked[df_ranked['cum_ratio']<=0.8]['feature'].to_list()
display(df_ranked, key_features)
```

```python
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
fig, ax1 = plt.subplots(figsize=(7,4))
ax2 = ax1.twinx()
ax1.bar(df_ranked['feature'], df_ranked['impact'], color = 'gray')
ax2.plot(df_ranked['feature'], df_ranked['cum_ratio'], marker = 'o')
ax1.set_title("Pareto Analysis of Feature Impact")
ax1.set_xlabel("Feature")
ax1.set_ylabel("Impact")
ax2.set_ylabel("Cumulative Ratio")
ax1.grid(False)
ax2.grid(False)
ax2.axhline(0.8, color='gray', linestyle='--', linewidth=2)
```
